<body>
    <%- include('../partials/header') -%>
    <div class="bg"></div><br>
    <h1 style="color:black; font-size: 300%;">SPECIALITIES PAGE: RESPIRATORY MEDICINE</h1><br>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="card bg-light text-dark">
            <h4>PNEUMONIA</h4>
            <p>Pneumonia is a generic diagnosis. 
                Even though there are different types of pneumonia, the way that the condition affects the lungs is similar in each one.
                With pneumonia, a virus, bacteria, or another infectious agent causes the tiny air sacs in the lungs (alveoli) to fill with fluid or pus. 
                These air sacs are what help exchange oxygen and other gases between the air that is breathed in and the blood.
                When these sacs are filled with fluid, the bodyâ€™s ability to exchange gases is reduced.
            </p>
        </div><br>                
        <div class="card bg-light text-dark">
            <div class="card-body"><strong> Symptoms</strong>
                <ul>
                    <li> - Fever</li>
                    <li> - Chills</li>
                    <li> - A cough that produces phlegm</li>
                    <li> - Shortness of breath</li>
                    <li> - Chest pain when you cough or breathe</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div><br>
        <button onclick="prediction()" type="button" class="btn btn-dark">Pneumonia Prediction</button>
        <div id="predict" style="display: none;">
            <strong>Upload your X-Ray file below</strong><br>
            <form action="/predict" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data">
                <div class="custom-file mb-3">
                    <input type="file" class="custom-file-input" id="customFile" name="file">
                    <label class="custom-file-label" for="customFile">Choose file</label>
                </div>
                <input type="submit" class="btn btn-success" value="Upload"><br>
               
                
                
                
                  
            </form>
            <% if (message) { %>
                <p><%= message %></p>
            <% } %>

            
            <% var predictionStr = JSON.stringify(prediction); %>
            <p>Prediction: <%= predictionStr %></p>
            <% if (predictionStr == '{"predicted_class":"PNEUMONIA"}') { %>
                <div class="card card-body alert alert-danger"><center>POSITIVE. The patient might have the disease.</center></div>
            <% } if (predictionStr == '{"predicted_class":"NORMAL"}') { %>
                <div class="card card-body alert alert-success"><center>NEGATIVE. The patient is healthy.</center></div>
            <% } %>

            
               

        </div>
    </div>
        <script>
            function prediction() {
              var p = document.getElementById("predict");
              if (p.style.display === "none") {
                p.style.display = "block";
              } else {
                p.style.display = "none";
              }
            }
        </script>
        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/jquery@3.6.3/dist/jquery.slim.min.js"></script>
        <script>$(".custom-file-input").on("change", function() {
            var fileName = $(this).val().split("\\").pop();
            $(this).siblings(".custom-file-label").addClass("selected").html(fileName);
            });
        </script>
